amona Blue\"\n| Joey King featuring Kelli King\n|-\n| 2011\n| \"[[Mean (song)|Mean]]\"\n| [[Taylor Swift]]\n|-\n| 2018\n| \"[[Sue Me]]\"\n| [[Sabrina Carpenter]]\n|-\n| 2019\n| \"[[Tongue Tied (Marshmello, Yungblud and Blackbear song)|Tongue Tied]]\"\n| [[Marshmello]], [[Yungblud]] and [[Blackbear (musician)|Blackbear]]\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n! class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2009\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[30th Young Artist Awards|Young Artist Awards]]\n| Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Guest Starring Young Actress\n| ''[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role \u2013 Young Actress\n| ''[[Horton Hears a Who!]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2010\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[31st Young Artist Awards|Young Artist Awards]]\n| Best Performance in a TV Series (Comedy or Drama) \u2013 Supporting Young Actress\n| ''[[Anatomy of Hope (TV series)|Anatomy of Hope]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role \u2013 Young Actor/Actress\n| ''[[Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2011\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[32nd Young Artist Awards|Young Artist Awards]]\n| [[32nd Young Artist Awards#Best Performance in a Feature Film - Leading Young Actress Ten and Under|Best Performance in a Feature Film \u2013 Leading Young Actress Ten and Under]]\n| ''[[Ramona and Beezus]]''\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/noms32.html |title=32nd Annual Young Artist Awards \u2013 Nominations / Special Awards |publisher=The Young Artist Foundation |year=2011 |accessdate=March 14, 2011 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130808150433/http://www.youngartistawards.org/noms32.html |archivedate=August 8, 2013 |df= }}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Guest Starring Young Actress Age 