us]]'' and other birds ''[[Eoneornis|Eoneornis australis]]'', ''[[Eutelornis|Eutelornis patagonicus]]'', ''[[Anisolornis|Anisolornis excavatus]]'', ''[[Protibis|Protibis cnemialis]]'', ''[[Opisthodactylus|Opisthodactylus patagonicus]]'', ''[[Liptornis|Liptornis hesternus]]'', and many mammals by {{small|{{smallcaps|A. M. Albino. 1996. Snakes from the Miocene of Patagonia (Argentina) Part II: The Colubroidea. Neues Jahrbuch f\u00fcr Geologie und Pal\u00e4ontologie, Abhandlungen 200(3):353-360}}}} & {{smallcaps|{{cite LSA |last=Vizca\u00edno |first=Sergio F. |last2=Kay |first2=Richard F. |last3=Bargo |first3=Susana |year=2012 |title=Early Miocene Paleobiology in Patagonia: High-Latitude Paleocommunities of the Santa Cruz Formation |url=https://books.google.com.co/books?id=3Ce0uINITb4C |publisher=[[Cambridge University|Cambridge University Press]] {{ISBN|9780521194617}} |pages=1\u2013370 |accessdate=2017-10-21}}}}}} || align=center | <ref>[http://fossilworks.org/bridge.pl?a=collectionSearch&collection_no=27313 Fossilworks]</ref><ref>[http://fossilworks.org/bridge.pl?a=collectionSearch&collection_no=176570 Fossilworks]</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n=== Bibliography ===\n<!--Most recent publications first-->\n* {{cite LSA |last=Barbi\u00e8re |first=Franck |last2=Ortiz |first2=Pablo E. |last3=Pardi\u00f1as |first3=Ulyses F.J. |year=2018 |title=The oldest sigmodontine rodent revisited and the age of the first South American cricetids |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/329716532_The_oldest_sigmodontine_rodent_revisited_and_the_age_of_the_first_South_American_cricetids |journal=[[Journal of Paleontology]] |volume=Online edition |issue=_ |pages=_ |accessdate=2019-02-11}}\n* {{cite LSA |last=Barbi\u00e8re |first=Franck |last2=Cruz |first2=Laura E. |last3=Ortiz |first3=Pablo E. |last4=Pardi\u00f1as |first4=Ulyses F. J. |year=2016 |title=A new genus of Sigmodontinae (Mammalia, Rodentia, Cricetidae) from the Pliocene of Central Argentina |url=h